{"lastModified":1770118737468,"uri":"c::9938368400::vessel::f7365760-3a25-11f0-bfc9-c38d371d38e7","yachtType":["Power Catamaran","Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: \nSummer - Corsica, French Riviera & Monaco, Italy - North (mainland), Italy - Sardinia, Italy - Sicily, Italy - South (mainland), Provence Coast & Marseille\n\nStep aboard M/Y GIGI, the newest gem in the Sunreef 70 Power line, launched in 2025 and crafted to impress even the most discerning charter guests. More than just a yacht, GIGI is a floating art gallery, where contemporary design meets timeless elegance.\n\nFrom the moment you arrive, her generous volumes, curated interiors, and fluid indoor-outdoor living spaces set the tone for an experience that is both luxurious and intimate. Think panoramic sea views, sun-drenched lounges, and the soft touch of bespoke materials underfoot.\n\nWhether you're sipping cocktails on the flybridge, discovering secret coves by Seabob, or unwinding in one of the four serene staterooms, GIGI delivers effortless style with a sense of warmth and soul.\n\nAs one of the finest showcases of Sunreef’s signature savoir-faire at sea, GIGI offers a truly immersive way to experience the brand’s world-renowned craftsmanship and innovation.\n\nThis is not just a holiday, it’s your personal escape, sculpted in sunlight and sea breeze.","blueprint":{"name":"GIGI","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::f7365760-3a25-11f0-bfc9-c38d371d38e7::assets::b3242ce0-45f2-11f0-897e-4d47296a31b7/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::f7365760-3a25-11f0-bfc9-c38d371d38e7::assets::b32390a0-45f2-11f0-897e-4d47296a31b7/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::f7365760-3a25-11f0-bfc9-c38d371d38e7::assets::b3303ad0-45f2-11f0-897e-4d47296a31b7/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::f7365760-3a25-11f0-bfc9-c38d371d38e7::assets::b3317350-45f2-11f0-897e-4d47296a31b7/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::f7365760-3a25-11f0-bfc9-c38d371d38e7::assets::b32cb860